'''Robert Watts''' ([[May 23]], [[1930s#1938|1938]]&ndash;[[September 30]], [[2024]])<ref name="THR" /> was a production manager on [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''A New Hope'']], an associate producer on [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']], and a co-producer on [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']]. He also played [[Lieutenant]] [[Blanaid]] in ''Return of the Jedi''.

[[Jeremy Bulloch]], who played [[Boba Fett]] for most of ''The Empire Strikes Back'' and all of ''Return of the Jedi'', is Watts' half-brother.<ref name="Lucasfilm obituary" />

